<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Welcome to UFCU</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#eef2f7;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#eef2f7;padding:30px 0;">
<tr><td align="center">

<table width="650" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#ffffff;border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">

<!-- HEADER -->
<tr>
<td style="background:#0b2e6b;padding:20px;">
<table width="100%"><tr>
<td style="color:white;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;">UFCU Credit Union</td>
<td align="right">
<img src="data:image/png;base64,#[output text/plain --- dw::core::Binaries::toBase64(readUrl('classpath://ufculogo.png', 'application/octet-stream'))]" alt="UFCU Logo" style="height:60px;display:block;">
</td>
</tr></table>
</td>
</tr>

<!-- BANNER -->
<tr>
<td style="background:#f3f6fb;text-align:center;padding:30px;">
<h2 style="margin:0;color:#0b2e6b;">Welcome to UFCU</h2>
<p style="margin-top:8px;color:#555;font-size:14px;">Your trusted financial partner</p>
</td>
</tr>

<!-- EMAIL BODY -->
<tr>
<td style="padding:40px;color:#333;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;">
<p>Dear <strong>#[payload.partyRecord.partyName]</strong>,</p>
<p>Congratulations! Your checking account with <strong>UFCU</strong> has been successfully created. We are excited to have you as a member of our credit union.</p>
<p><strong>Account Number:</strong> #[vars.accountNumber]</p>
<p>With your new account you can enjoy:</p>
<ul>
<li>Online and Mobile Banking</li>
<li>Secure money transfers</li>
<li>Bill payments</li>
<li>24/7 account access</li>
</ul>
<p>You can log in anytime to manage your finances easily.</p>
<table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:30px 0;">
<tr>
<td style="background:#0b2e6b;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:5px;">
<a href="https://www.ufcu.org" style="color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;">Access Online Banking</a>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<p>Thank you for choosing <strong>UFCU</strong>. We look forward to serving you.</p>
</td>
</tr>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<tr>
<td style="background:#f4f6f9;text-align:center;padding:25px;font-size:12px;color:#666;line-height:1.6;">
<p style="margin:0;">&copy; 2026 UFCU Credit Union</p>
<p style="margin-top:6px;">Secure &bull; Trusted &bull; Member Focused</p>
</td>
</tr>

</table>
</td></tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>


